#  L5i)zShow all available commands.u   âš¡ Mack Bot â€” Command Centeru¨   

**ðŸ‘¤ Player Commands**

> `!status` â€” Check your verification progress
> `!list` â€” View live esports roster for this channel
> `!help` â€” Show this help menu

uP   

**ðŸ“‹ Verification Steps**

> **` 1 `** Upload **4 unique screenshots** in <#uK   >
> **` 2 `** Wait for mod approval âœ…
> **` 3 `** Verify your squad in <#z$>
> **` 4 `** Submit team name in <#z>
rx  u0  

**ðŸ”§ Admin Commands**

> `!approve @user` â€” Approve a user's verification
> `!reject @user [reason]` â€” Reject with optional reason
> `!blacklist @user [reason]` â€” Permanently block a user
> `!unblacklist @user` â€” Remove from blacklist
> `!stats` â€” View verification statistics
> `!setrole @Role` â€” Set the verified role
> `!setwelcome #channel` â€” Set welcome channel
> `!resetuser @user` â€” Reset a user's verification data

**ðŸ† Scrim Admin Commands**

> `!scrim_setup @Role <slots>` â€” Setup scrim registration panel
> `!open` â€” Manually unlock the registration button
> `!close` â€” Manually lock the registration button
> `!removeslot <slot_number>` â€” Force remove a team from a slot
> `!announce @Role [msg]` â€” Announce registration is open
> `!wipe` â€” Wipe roster and reset panel
